title: Enterprise -- Selling of Terri Gibbs -- 1983
description: You see a singer Terri Gibbs and how her manager and the record company MCA, is trying to promote her new song. You see the process from the editors from the music industry to calling radio stations in hopes of playing her new song. Song that is promoting is "Ashes to Ashes" which went up so far, then suddenly drop off the charts.
